title: Shayan Sheikh
text: Shayan Sheikh (born 5 May 1998) is a Pakistani <a href="cricket">cricket</a>er. He made his <a href="List%20A%20cricket">List A</a> debut for <a href="Khan%20Research%20Laboratories%20cricket%20team">Khan Research Laboratories</a> in the <a href="2017%E2%80%9318%20Departmental%20One%20Day%20Cup">2017–18 Departmental One Day Cup</a> on 9 January 2018. He made his <a href="first-class%20cricket">first-class</a> debut for Khan Research Laboratories in the <a href="2018%E2%80%9319%20Quaid-e-Azam%20Trophy">2018–19 Quaid-e-Azam Trophy</a> on 19 November 2018.
